WEBVTT

00:01:33.450 --> 00:01:34.979
[OVERDO]

00:01:35.259 --> 00:01:37.700
[Episode 13]

00:01:44.039 --> 00:01:45.580
[Tung Teh Road]

00:01:45.580 --> 00:01:48.580
[Hong Fang Bank]

00:01:46.200 --> 00:01:46.950
Search the place!

00:01:46.950 --> 00:01:47.410
Search!

00:01:47.479 --> 00:01:48.310
You can't go in!

00:01:48.310 --> 00:01:49.310
Get out of the way!

00:01:58.950 --> 00:01:59.560
Young Master Qingyi.

00:01:59.560 --> 00:02:00.560
Why are you throwing your weight around here, Young Master Qingyi?

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:01.490
What do you want?

00:02:06.680 --> 00:02:09.080
The Zunlan Elite Club of Hong Fang Bank

00:02:09.400 --> 00:02:11.240
Often hosts gatherings for the rich and influential,

00:02:11.240 --> 00:02:12.440
And those gatherings

00:02:12.630 --> 00:02:15.000
Are always graced by the presence of beautiful women across the country.

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:15.910
Young Master Huo,

00:02:15.910 --> 00:02:16.840
Am I right?

00:02:18.800 --> 00:02:20.150
At Hong Fang Bank,

00:02:20.750 --> 00:02:22.240
We provide the highest quality service

00:02:22.240 --> 00:02:24.150
To our most distinguished clients

00:02:24.150 --> 00:02:25.960
By inviting Nancheng's top entertainers,

00:02:25.960 --> 00:02:27.190
Movie stars,

00:02:27.910 --> 00:02:29.440
And registered courtesans

00:02:29.590 --> 00:02:30.650
To share in the fun.

00:02:31.630 --> 00:02:34.230
This is common knowledge within the industry.

00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:36.170
What's wrong with that?

00:02:37.190 --> 00:02:38.190
Young Master Huo,

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:41.190
Maybe you should have your men look into it,

00:02:41.190 --> 00:02:42.360
So you don't accidentally

00:02:42.360 --> 00:02:44.120
Invite someone you shouldn't.

00:02:44.400 --> 00:02:46.150
What the hell are you going on about?

00:02:46.150 --> 00:02:47.400
I used to give you some leeway

00:02:47.400 --> 00:02:48.800
Because we were in-laws.

00:02:49.560 --> 00:02:51.520
But now your Murong family wouldn't even show your faces,

00:02:51.520 --> 00:02:53.520
Trying to break off the engagement with just a letter.

00:02:53.520 --> 00:02:55.960
You've not only humiliated our Huo family in public,

00:02:55.960 --> 00:02:58.430
But you've also taken advantage of our family's 5 planes for nothing.

00:02:58.430 --> 00:03:00.280
Do you really think I, Huo Zongqi, am a pushover

00:03:00.280 --> 00:03:02.240
That you can push around however you like?

00:03:02.240 --> 00:03:03.030
So annoying.

00:03:19.680 --> 00:03:20.470
Too bad—

00:03:21.240 --> 00:03:22.840
My gun never misses.

00:03:27.310 --> 00:03:28.280
Murong Qingyi.

00:03:28.750 --> 00:03:30.079
Have you lost your mind?

00:03:31.430 --> 00:03:32.760
Guess whether this shot

00:03:34.030 --> 00:03:35.470
Will miss again.

00:03:40.360 --> 00:03:41.290
Keep searching!

00:03:41.800 --> 00:03:43.200
I'd like to see who dares!

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:48.000
Do you think the Huo family is somewhere you can just walk in

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:49.730
And walk out whenever you want?

00:04:28.070 --> 00:04:29.000
What's going on?

00:04:33.390 --> 00:04:34.990
Ye Zhihong has gone missing.

00:04:35.040 --> 00:04:38.170
A Hong Fang Bank cash bundle strap was found at the scene.

00:04:38.390 --> 00:04:40.600
It's just a strap used to bundle banknotes.

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:42.950
This kind of paper can be found everywhere.

00:04:42.950 --> 00:04:44.310
Even though it has the bank's stamp on it,

00:04:44.310 --> 00:04:45.840
It doesn't prove anything.

00:04:46.000 --> 00:04:47.240
Don't think you can just make up some excuse

00:04:47.240 --> 00:04:49.040
To search our Huo family's bank.

00:04:54.159 --> 00:04:55.600
Where's my sapphire?

00:05:00.430 --> 00:05:02.190
Wasn't it just there a moment ago?

00:05:02.190 --> 00:05:03.240
That's an extremely rare

00:05:03.240 --> 00:05:04.560
Kashmir sapphire.

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:06.430
That won't do.

00:05:09.390 --> 00:05:10.750
The Huo family

00:05:11.160 --> 00:05:12.420
Has to answer for this.

00:05:13.830 --> 00:05:14.720
Murong Qingyi.

00:05:15.310 --> 00:05:17.000
Our families' relationships and interests

00:05:17.000 --> 00:05:18.400
Are deeply intertwined.

00:05:19.120 --> 00:05:21.920
Have you thought about the consequences of doing this?

00:05:21.920 --> 00:05:24.320
Don't end up being dragged to our Huo family

00:05:24.600 --> 00:05:26.330
To grovel and apologize again.

00:05:26.480 --> 00:05:27.340
Consequences?

00:05:28.720 --> 00:05:31.380
Your Huo family has provoked our Murong family.

00:05:31.680 --> 00:05:32.950
Now, as for Hong Fang Bank,

00:05:32.950 --> 00:05:33.920
I can come

00:05:33.920 --> 00:05:35.040
And go as I please.

00:05:35.870 --> 00:05:37.270
That's the consequence.

00:05:42.310 --> 00:05:43.600
Go upstairs and search!

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:44.190
Yes!

00:05:52.190 --> 00:05:53.360
Wait, you can't go in!

00:05:53.360 --> 00:05:55.159
-Move aside! -Get out of the way!

00:06:11.040 --> 00:06:12.640
Send in more men and weapons.

00:06:13.430 --> 00:06:14.830
Seal off all exits.

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:17.730
Don't let a single one of them get away.

00:06:18.160 --> 00:06:18.540
Yes.

00:06:18.560 --> 00:06:19.220
-Yes. -Yes.

00:06:26.560 --> 00:06:28.000
Let the Huo family bank staff leave.

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:28.630
-Search carefully. -Who gave you permission

00:06:28.630 --> 00:06:29.190
-Search! -to come in?

00:06:29.190 --> 00:06:30.250
What are you doing?

00:06:30.480 --> 00:06:31.540
Let me go! Let me go!

00:06:32.240 --> 00:06:32.750
Let go!

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:34.600
Anything?

00:06:34.720 --> 00:06:35.250
Nothing.

00:06:35.480 --> 00:06:36.159
-Get out. -Nothing here.

00:06:36.159 --> 00:06:37.290
Take me to the vault.

00:06:37.680 --> 00:06:38.810
You can't go inside!

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:39.430
Let's go.

00:06:39.430 --> 00:06:40.630
You can't go inside!

00:06:41.560 --> 00:06:42.510
What's going on?

00:06:43.220 --> 00:06:44.750
Why are they kicking us out?

00:06:48.600 --> 00:06:50.330
Why are they suddenly closing?

00:07:03.390 --> 00:07:05.000
Why won't they let us make a deposit?

00:07:05.000 --> 00:07:06.000
I haven't finished my transaction yet.

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:07.120
Give us an explanation.

00:07:07.120 --> 00:07:09.070
We just want to make deposits.

00:07:13.190 --> 00:07:13.990
Young Master.

00:07:14.190 --> 00:07:15.190
We found nothing.

00:07:15.830 --> 00:07:17.800
The Huo family has sent people to surround the bank.

00:07:17.800 --> 00:07:19.000
How should we get out?

00:07:22.310 --> 00:07:24.040
Every day I'm delayed is a day of interest I lose.

00:07:24.040 --> 00:07:25.900
Are you going to cover our losses?

00:07:26.310 --> 00:07:27.830
When did Ms. Ye go missing?

00:07:31.390 --> 00:07:32.920
Last night, on her way home,

00:07:33.120 --> 00:07:34.950
She was abducted by the Huo family

00:07:34.950 --> 00:07:36.810
And forced into an armored truck.

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:37.920
I'm afraid...

00:07:38.360 --> 00:07:40.020
It's that club you mentioned.

00:07:40.480 --> 00:07:41.409
I heard there are

00:07:41.560 --> 00:07:43.890
Many women of unknown backgrounds there.

00:07:44.630 --> 00:07:47.070
Do you remember those girls

00:07:47.480 --> 00:07:51.210
Who went missing from the orphanage that I mentioned to you before?

00:07:53.070 --> 00:07:55.730
Those girls of unknown backgrounds at that club

00:07:56.040 --> 00:07:57.370
Are from the orphanage.

00:08:00.240 --> 00:08:03.270
They've been groomed since childhood to be sold to the powerful and wealthy.

00:08:03.270 --> 00:08:05.400
They're never fed enough to stay full,

00:08:05.430 --> 00:08:07.160
Kept thin and frail,

00:08:13.630 --> 00:08:16.630
And beaten until their bodies are covered in bruises.

00:08:19.800 --> 00:08:21.400
When they reach the right age

00:08:21.480 --> 00:08:22.610
To be "shipped out,"

00:08:24.070 --> 00:08:27.000
They'd first be put into ice-cold water to be frozen.

00:08:47.320 --> 00:08:48.850
Why are you telling me this?

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:51.890
Are you trying to get me to feel sorry for them?

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:52.510
Tell me.

00:08:53.480 --> 00:08:55.340
How do you plan to use me this time?

00:08:57.150 --> 00:08:58.880
The one auctioning those girls

00:08:59.200 --> 00:09:00.440
Is the Elite Club.

00:09:08.600 --> 00:09:09.730
We'd better focus on

00:09:10.200 --> 00:09:11.730
How to get out of here first.

00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:17.260
If a problem can be solved with money,

00:09:18.550 --> 00:09:19.880
Then it's not a problem.

00:09:37.870 --> 00:09:38.550
Look up!

00:09:40.190 --> 00:09:41.910
[Zarry Grand Hotel]

00:09:43.750 --> 00:09:45.350
Stop them! Hurry! Stop them!

00:10:27.150 --> 00:10:29.030
-Freeze! Stop there! -Stop!

00:10:29.270 --> 00:10:30.530
-Stop there! -Freeze!

00:10:30.840 --> 00:10:32.200
You sure aren't shy about

00:10:32.200 --> 00:10:33.200
Spending the Fang family's money,

00:10:33.200 --> 00:10:34.200
Miss Ren, are you?

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:37.080
That wasn't the Fang family's money.

00:10:37.080 --> 00:10:38.840
It was dirty money I got from

00:10:38.840 --> 00:10:40.700
Shorting Hong Fang Bank's stock.

00:10:40.750 --> 00:10:42.080
The Huo family has done all kinds of evil.

00:10:42.080 --> 00:10:45.010
It's about time they gave something back to society.

00:10:56.790 --> 00:10:58.080
Look, this whole mess has caused you

00:10:58.080 --> 00:11:00.410
So much trouble and cost you so much money.

00:11:00.960 --> 00:11:02.550
Do you want me to talk to Qingyu

00:11:02.550 --> 00:11:03.870
And have him reimburse you some of it?

00:11:03.870 --> 00:11:04.550
After all,

00:11:05.200 --> 00:11:07.120
Losing a little money to his fiancée

00:11:07.120 --> 00:11:08.670
In order to find the woman he loves

00:11:08.670 --> 00:11:10.000
Isn't really a big deal.

00:11:13.270 --> 00:11:15.200
I'm afraid Ms. Ye was probably sold

00:11:15.200 --> 00:11:17.130
Together with this batch of girls.

00:11:17.240 --> 00:11:19.550
But the Huo family has always been known for recruiting orphaned girls.

00:11:19.550 --> 00:11:22.280
Why did they target Ms. Ye of all people this time?

00:11:22.480 --> 00:11:23.410
Not surprising.

00:11:23.720 --> 00:11:24.750
Master Huo

00:11:25.000 --> 00:11:26.550
Already took a special liking to Ms. Ye

00:11:26.550 --> 00:11:28.410
When the aviation school opened.

00:11:40.720 --> 00:11:43.360
For those lackeys, taking a little risk

00:11:43.670 --> 00:11:45.470
To please Master Huo is nothing.

00:11:47.360 --> 00:11:48.630
That's truly disgusting.

00:11:48.630 --> 00:11:49.510
Disgusting?

00:11:49.870 --> 00:11:51.470
Are you worried about Ms. Ye,

00:11:51.630 --> 00:11:53.430
Or are you worried about Qingyu?

00:11:54.360 --> 00:11:55.030
Pull over.

00:11:55.150 --> 00:11:56.610
I need to go to Fang's shop.

00:11:56.630 --> 00:11:57.270
What for?

00:11:57.840 --> 00:11:59.640
To take them all down, of course.

00:12:08.150 --> 00:12:09.360
How amusing.

00:12:10.360 --> 00:12:12.030
You won't catch them in the act,

00:12:12.030 --> 00:12:14.960
But you sure don't hesitate to throw yourself at him.

00:12:19.000 --> 00:12:20.060
What's that about?

00:12:20.840 --> 00:12:21.910
I just want to see

00:12:21.910 --> 00:12:24.910
What throwing yourself at someone really looks like.

00:12:26.000 --> 00:12:28.400
I simply don't see eye to eye with her, okay?

00:12:45.030 --> 00:12:46.080
Miss Fang.

00:12:46.270 --> 00:12:48.440
I heard you guys pulled off another big stunt.

00:12:48.440 --> 00:12:50.440
Whenever you two get together,

00:12:50.440 --> 00:12:52.030
You end up making a huge scene—

00:12:52.030 --> 00:12:53.870
Like you won't stop until one of you is dead, huh?

00:12:53.870 --> 00:12:56.150
Jumping off airplanes, jumping off trains,

00:12:56.150 --> 00:12:57.610
Throwing money around...

00:12:57.910 --> 00:12:59.710
What are you planning to do next?

00:13:00.510 --> 00:13:01.510
Down to business.

00:13:12.480 --> 00:13:14.960
At one of the sewer exits you had under surveillance,

00:13:14.960 --> 00:13:16.230
Tao found a glass bead.

00:13:16.910 --> 00:13:18.120
It does prove

00:13:18.390 --> 00:13:21.390
That the inside of the vault connects directly to the sewer.

00:13:21.390 --> 00:13:23.850
I asked Tasia to keep an eye on the orphanage,

00:13:23.870 --> 00:13:25.270
And she discovered today

00:13:25.630 --> 00:13:27.480
That the Huo family was planning to

00:13:27.480 --> 00:13:30.000
Send people in through the Dongjiadu entrance tonight.

00:13:30.000 --> 00:13:31.390
We don't have much time left.

00:13:31.390 --> 00:13:32.720
How should we save them?

00:13:36.080 --> 00:13:37.880
By entering the game ourselves.

00:15:32.270 --> 00:15:33.200
Is anyone there?

00:15:34.960 --> 00:15:35.890
Is anyone there?

00:15:53.270 --> 00:15:53.870
Huo...

00:15:55.270 --> 00:15:56.120
Master Huo.

00:15:58.630 --> 00:16:00.030
What are you trying to do?

00:16:00.630 --> 00:16:02.200
You just took the drug.

00:16:03.150 --> 00:16:05.350
You won't have any strength for a while.

00:16:05.720 --> 00:16:07.480
As long as you do as I say,

00:16:08.480 --> 00:16:10.810
I'll make sure you experience pure bliss.

00:16:15.510 --> 00:16:16.870
And if I refuse?

00:16:17.390 --> 00:16:20.150
Then I'm afraid I can't let you leave here alive.

00:16:28.910 --> 00:16:29.790
You should know

00:16:30.390 --> 00:16:31.600
That human trafficking

00:16:31.600 --> 00:16:32.660
Is a serious crime.

00:16:43.030 --> 00:16:45.120
Do you really think you can escape?

00:16:45.790 --> 00:16:47.650
The only thing leaving here today

00:16:47.720 --> 00:16:49.480
Will be a corpse!

00:16:52.960 --> 00:16:53.840
Someone!

00:16:54.240 --> 00:16:56.840
Lock her up in the vault's dungeon!

00:17:22.030 --> 00:17:22.640
Qingyu.

00:17:24.480 --> 00:17:25.310
We've searched everywhere in Hong Fang Bank

00:17:25.310 --> 00:17:26.569
That we could get into,

00:17:27.000 --> 00:17:28.310
But we couldn't find Ms. Ye.

00:17:28.310 --> 00:17:28.770
Then...

00:17:29.070 --> 00:17:31.530
Then what about the places we can't get into?

00:17:31.590 --> 00:17:33.110
The only place we can't get into

00:17:33.110 --> 00:17:34.310
Is the Elite Club.

00:17:37.720 --> 00:17:39.110
I've had someone check on

00:17:39.110 --> 00:17:40.200
The specific event schedule

00:17:40.200 --> 00:17:41.730
For this Huo family's club.

00:17:42.830 --> 00:17:44.000
Young Masters.

00:17:44.830 --> 00:17:47.290
I found out about a regular at the Elite Club.

00:17:47.350 --> 00:17:47.880
Who is it?

00:17:48.270 --> 00:17:49.880
The young master of the Zheng family

00:17:49.880 --> 00:17:51.200
Who owns Donglian Canning Factory,

00:17:51.200 --> 00:17:52.000
Zheng Jialin.

00:18:00.550 --> 00:18:01.480
Zheng Jialin...

00:18:05.770 --> 00:18:07.700
[Tianyun Restaurant]

00:18:07.030 --> 00:18:08.200
Welcome, distinguished guests.

00:18:08.200 --> 00:18:08.750
Welcome.

00:18:09.350 --> 00:18:10.070
Welcome.

00:18:10.550 --> 00:18:11.110
Welcome.

00:18:17.020 --> 00:18:20.150
[Celestial Casino]

00:18:29.110 --> 00:18:29.960
Pair of Queens.

00:18:29.960 --> 00:18:31.070
Mr. Zheng.

00:18:31.590 --> 00:18:32.650
Thank you for that.

00:18:35.830 --> 00:18:37.310
Why is my luck so bad today?

00:18:38.270 --> 00:18:39.400
Young Master Zheng.

00:18:39.880 --> 00:18:41.510
You win some, you lose some.

00:18:41.680 --> 00:18:42.810
A bad run at the start

00:18:43.000 --> 00:18:44.550
Doesn't mean it'll stay that way.

00:18:44.550 --> 00:18:46.010
Let's play another round.

00:18:47.030 --> 00:18:47.830
Zheng Jialin,

00:18:48.440 --> 00:18:49.550
Giving up already?

00:18:53.110 --> 00:18:53.680
Come on,

00:18:53.880 --> 00:18:55.680
Deal the cards. Let's continue.

00:18:57.110 --> 00:18:58.030
Then we'll

00:18:58.110 --> 00:18:59.570
Put it on your tab as usual.

00:19:13.030 --> 00:19:14.720
I'll have Lin deal the cards for you.

00:19:14.720 --> 00:19:15.310
Maybe that'll bring you some better luck.

00:19:15.310 --> 00:19:16.110
Sure.

00:19:16.110 --> 00:19:16.710
Come here.

00:19:34.200 --> 00:19:35.510
I helped you out this time.

00:19:35.510 --> 00:19:36.970
How do you plan to repay me?

00:19:38.400 --> 00:19:39.440
Once this is done,

00:19:39.680 --> 00:19:41.940
I'll give you a generous gift, of course.

00:19:42.400 --> 00:19:44.030
Don't keep me in suspense.

00:19:44.400 --> 00:19:46.920
Zheng Jialin may not be a big shot,

00:19:47.240 --> 00:19:48.440
But if things get out of hand,

00:19:48.440 --> 00:19:49.970
It won't be easy to clean up.

00:19:50.240 --> 00:19:52.770
All that talk of a big gift is just empty words.

00:19:54.920 --> 00:19:56.240
Buy me dinner first.

00:19:57.270 --> 00:19:58.200
Not tonight.

00:19:58.480 --> 00:20:00.240
I have something important to take care of.

00:20:00.240 --> 00:20:01.500
Something important?

00:20:02.310 --> 00:20:03.960
What could possibly be so important

00:20:03.960 --> 00:20:07.090
That it's occupying the mind of our cold-hearted, aloof

00:20:07.160 --> 00:20:08.790
Young Master Qingyi?

00:20:12.160 --> 00:20:13.440
Cut it out.

00:20:13.920 --> 00:20:16.320
Stop showing off your charms in front of me.

00:20:18.880 --> 00:20:20.030
How unromantic.

00:20:20.310 --> 00:20:21.110
Two pairs!

00:20:21.400 --> 00:20:22.400
A straight.

00:20:27.550 --> 00:20:28.310
It's time.

00:20:28.310 --> 00:20:29.110
Go now.

00:20:32.640 --> 00:20:32.960
Alright.

00:20:32.960 --> 00:20:33.640
Mr. Li.

00:20:33.640 --> 00:20:34.700
I must've owed you.

00:20:35.240 --> 00:20:35.920
Round it up.

00:20:36.400 --> 00:20:37.880
Add another 400 and make it 1,000.

00:20:37.880 --> 00:20:40.160
Let's play another round. I don't believe in this bad luck.

00:20:40.160 --> 00:20:41.160
Zheng Jialin,

00:20:45.440 --> 00:20:47.370
You've got no money left to gamble.

00:20:52.960 --> 00:20:53.890
What do you mean?

00:20:54.350 --> 00:20:55.960
You've lost your family's canning factory

00:20:55.960 --> 00:20:57.350
To our casino.

00:20:58.030 --> 00:20:58.590
Here,

00:20:58.790 --> 00:21:01.160
You signed and put your fingerprint on it yourself.

00:21:01.160 --> 00:21:02.960
No, I didn't!

00:21:03.270 --> 00:21:04.870
You guys forced me to sign it!

00:21:05.880 --> 00:21:07.010
Young Master Zheng.

00:21:07.030 --> 00:21:08.310
A bet is a bet.

00:21:08.590 --> 00:21:10.190
Let's not make this awkward.

00:21:10.310 --> 00:21:11.270
Bullshit!

00:21:13.480 --> 00:21:15.810
I can give the canning factory back to you.

00:21:15.920 --> 00:21:16.750
But

00:21:17.790 --> 00:21:18.790
On one condition.

00:21:26.010 --> 00:21:27.690
[Murong Residence]

00:21:40.240 --> 00:21:40.970
Where is she?

00:21:41.920 --> 00:21:44.450
Miss Fang only said she was going out for a bit.

00:21:44.880 --> 00:21:45.830
Did she say where she was going?

00:21:45.830 --> 00:21:46.790
No, she didn't.

00:21:47.350 --> 00:21:49.010
Didn't she leave with Qingyu?

00:21:50.440 --> 00:21:51.240
You may leave.

00:21:53.070 --> 00:21:53.920
Zheng Jialin said

00:21:53.920 --> 00:21:56.310
Tonight is the night the club holds its gathering.

00:21:56.310 --> 00:21:57.750
Could Miss Fang have...

00:22:03.510 --> 00:22:04.920
I need to go to Hong Fang Bank.

00:22:04.920 --> 00:22:05.480
Hurry up

00:22:05.480 --> 00:22:06.160
And inform Qingyu first...

00:22:06.160 --> 00:22:09.160
Didn't you say her business had nothing to do with you?

00:22:53.030 --> 00:22:54.640
Good thing you've got sharp eyes.

00:22:54.640 --> 00:22:56.030
That woman was acting all sneaky.

00:22:56.030 --> 00:22:58.110
We really can't let her wander around out there.

00:22:58.110 --> 00:22:59.640
It just so happens Boss said he was short of two good ones.

00:22:59.640 --> 00:23:00.770
If we sell her today,

00:23:00.880 --> 00:23:02.590
We might even get a bonus.

00:23:03.030 --> 00:23:04.160
Time's running out.

00:23:04.590 --> 00:23:06.030
I'll lure them into taking me inside,

00:23:06.030 --> 00:23:07.760
Find out the girls' situation,

00:23:08.160 --> 00:23:09.310
And then figure out a way

00:23:09.310 --> 00:23:11.040
To leave route markers for you.

00:23:40.570 --> 00:23:45.350
[Hong Fang Bank]

00:24:00.640 --> 00:24:01.550
This is Zheng Jialin's

00:24:01.550 --> 00:24:03.880
Club membership card and mask.

00:24:05.310 --> 00:24:07.400
You'd better think this through carefully, Young Master Qingyi.

00:24:07.400 --> 00:24:09.270
If your identity is exposed after you go in,

00:24:09.270 --> 00:24:11.130
Don't expect to make it out alive.

00:25:04.920 --> 00:25:05.960
Are you alright?

00:25:10.310 --> 00:25:12.720
Help me. Help me.

00:25:13.160 --> 00:25:16.640
-Help me. Help me. -Help me.

00:25:17.200 --> 00:25:18.000
Don't worry.

00:25:18.110 --> 00:25:19.440
Are there any new girls?

00:25:29.790 --> 00:25:30.640
Ms. Ye?

00:25:32.200 --> 00:25:33.000
Ye Zhihong?

00:25:55.830 --> 00:25:56.480
Ms. Ye.

00:25:57.000 --> 00:25:57.660
Ye Zhihong!

00:26:00.550 --> 00:26:01.270
You guys,

00:26:01.590 --> 00:26:02.750
Go bring out the goods.

00:26:02.750 --> 00:26:03.280
Yes, sir.

00:26:33.590 --> 00:26:34.550
VIP No. 9.

00:26:35.400 --> 00:26:37.310
Please move to the VIP channel.

00:26:38.110 --> 00:26:40.110
So he's the legendary No. 9.

00:26:40.400 --> 00:26:43.330
I heard those with single-digit numbers are all veteran-level figures,

00:26:43.330 --> 00:26:45.030
[9]

00:26:43.640 --> 00:26:44.700
And their statuses

00:26:44.720 --> 00:26:46.580
Are exceptionally prestigious.

00:26:46.960 --> 00:26:47.790
Distinguished guest,

00:26:47.790 --> 00:26:48.790
Please follow me.

00:27:06.240 --> 00:27:07.170
This way please.

00:27:34.200 --> 00:27:34.730
This way.

00:28:02.550 --> 00:28:03.110
Sir,

00:28:03.440 --> 00:28:04.300
Please come in.

00:28:13.070 --> 00:28:13.590
Sir,

00:28:14.030 --> 00:28:15.240
This is Private Room No. 9.

00:28:15.240 --> 00:28:16.100
Please come in.

00:28:49.240 --> 00:28:50.900
They're here. It's starting.

00:29:11.310 --> 00:29:13.110
Distinguished guests,

00:29:13.310 --> 00:29:14.970
It's an honor to have you here.

00:29:15.070 --> 00:29:17.000
This Wang Yan is no ordinary woman.

00:29:17.030 --> 00:29:18.830
She started out as a petty thief,

00:29:18.880 --> 00:29:21.200
Stealing everything in her path without leaving a trace.

00:29:21.200 --> 00:29:22.960
Later, she was taken under the wing of the Huo family

00:29:22.960 --> 00:29:25.620
And got into the business of human trafficking.

00:30:22.640 --> 00:30:23.590
Ren Susu?

00:30:24.750 --> 00:30:25.750
How could it be her?

